### Health (pubblico)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/health


### Login mario
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3001/api/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "mario",
  "password": "mario123"
}

### Utente corrente (protetta)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/sessions/current

### Network (protetta) — linee, stazioni, segmenti
GET http://localhost:3001/api/network

### Nuova partita (protetta) — ritorna start/dest random
# @name newGame
POST http://localhost:3001/api/games

### Classifica (protetta)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/ranking

### Logout
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/sessions/current

